| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3336 — Recovery Inhibition (beast)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 74eabcd3-aee5-5040-8945-80761f1b786f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
